Mission Orders

The pirates and beasts along the Jagged Coast have been killing the locals.

Kill on the {@LinkCreature:11#4001#Red Lash crushers}, {@LinkCreature:11#4002#rovers}, and {@LinkCreature:11#4003#freebooters}, and {@LinkCreature:11#4004#spiketail kamaras}.

Report to Coordinator Rexana when mission is complete.
You've earned the thanks of the federation. Your guild is an inspiration to all!
